g.text: A Skolem individual constant, like RDF's blank nodes. See
an extension point to allow alternate names and internationalization for Skolem constants
an extension point to allow alternate names and
an extension point for specializations of the individual tag name.
an extension point for specializations of the data tag name.
Data terms may have mixed content from any namespace.
Individuals and literals (data) are simple, constant terms, and may be used in slot keys.
Skolem constants are simple constant terms,
but are not used in keys.
